original: Bernlöf, Albert Ragnar, andre stadsfogde, Göteborg, f. 5/1/92 i Gbg. G. 26 m. Astrid Hedvig Aurora Lindberg. Barn: Maud Astrid Aurora f. 27, Carl-Erik Ragnar 30. — Stud:ex. v. Gbgs h. latin 12, jur. kand. v. Upps. univ. 21. Tingstjg. v. Askims m. fl. här:rätt. Andre mag:not. v. Gbgs mag. 29, förste mag:not. 35, andre stadsfogde i Gbg fr. 45. Ordf. i tax:-nd ied. 37.
translated: Bernlöf, Albert Ragnar, second city bailiff, Gothenburg, born on January 5, 1892 in Gothenburg. Married on 1926 to Astrid Hedvig Aurora Lindberg, they have two children: Maud Astrid Aurora born on 1927 and Carl-Erik Ragnar born on 1930. He graduated with a Bachelor's degree in Latin from Gothenburg High School in 1912, and graduated with a law degree from Uppsala University in 1921. He served as a judicial clerk in Askims and other district courts and as a second notary in Gothenburg in 1929, first notary in 1935, and as a second city bailiff in Gothenburg from 1945. He was the chairman of the tax committee in 1937.
